methods

Returns the methods name of an object handle.

Syntax

c = methods(h)

Input argument

h

a handle object

Output argument

c

a cell of strings

Description

methods returns a cell of strings with methods name.

See also

isprop, ismethod.

History

Version Description
1.0.0 initial version

Author
